Class PlaceCardData

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.am52.json.request.PlaceCardData
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class PlaceCardData extends Object implements Serializable
The object representing the data for the placeStarterCard and placeCard methods. The placeStarterCard and placeCard methods require the id of the card and the visible face.
